## Get a post by id
GET http://localhost:3000/posts/37

## Update a post by id
PATCH http://localhost:3000/posts/38
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Post",
  "slug": "my-first-post",
  "content": "This is the content of my first post",
  "schema": "{\r\n  \"@context\": \"https:\/\/schema.org\",\r\n  \"@type\": \"BlogPosting\"\r\n}",
  "featuredImageUrl": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
  "tags": ["tag 1", "tag 6", "tag 8"],
  "metaOptions": { "metaValue": "{\"key\": \"value\", \"key2\": \"value2\"}" }
}

## Delete a post by id
DELETE http://localhost:3000/posts/36